     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xml:lang=\"fr-FR\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" lang=\"fr-FR\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Narratif généré : CodeSystem tre-r384-pratique-therapeutique-specifique-act-de-soin-amm</b></p><a name=\"tre-r384-pratique-therapeutique-specifique-act-de-soin-amm\"> </a><a name=\"hctre-r384-pratique-therapeutique-specifique-act-de-soin-amm\"> </a><div style=\"display: inline-block; background-color: #d9e0e7; padding: 6px; margin: 4px; border: 1px solid #8da1b4; border-radius: 5px; line-height: 60%\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">version : 2; Dernière mise à jour : 2026-05-05 20:12:15+0200; Langue : fr-FR</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px\">Profil: <a href=\"http://hl7.org/fhir/R4/shareablecodesystem.html\">Shareable CodeSystem</a></p></div><p><b>Propriétés</b></p><p><b>Cette terminologie de référence (CodeSystem) définit les propriétés suivantes pour ses concepts</b></p><table class=\"grid\"><tr><td><b>Nom</b></td><td><b>Code</b></td><td><b>URI</b></td><td><b>Type</b></td><td><b>Description</b></td></tr><tr><td>Date de Validité</td><td>dateValid</td><td>https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/concept-properties#dateValid</td><td>dateTime</td><td>date de validité d'un code concept</td></tr><tr><td>Date de mise à jour</td><td>dateMaj</td><td>https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/concept-properties#dateMaj</td><td>dateTime</td><td>Date de mise à jour d'un code concept</td></tr><tr><td>Date de fin</td><td>dateFin</td><td>https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/concept-properties#dateFin</td><td>dateTime</td><td>Date de fin d'exploitation d'un code concept</td></tr><tr><td>status</td><td>status</td><td>http://hl7.org/fhir/concept-properties#status</td><td>code</td><td>A code that indicates the status of the concept. Typical values are active, experimental, deprecated, and retired</td></tr><tr><td>deprecationDate</td><td>deprecationDate</td><td>http://hl7.org/fhir/concept-properties#deprecationDate</td><td>dateTime</td><td>The date at which a concept was deprecated. Concepts that are deprecated but not inactive can still be used, but their use is discouraged, and they should be expected to be made inactive in a future release. Property type is dateTime. Note that the status property may also be used to indicate that a concept is deprecated</td></tr><tr><td>retirementDate</td><td>retirementDate</td><td>http://hl7.org/fhir/concept-properties#retirementDate</td><td>dateTime</td><td>The date at which a concept was retired</td></tr></table><p><b>Concepts</b></p><p>This case-insensitive code system <code>https://smt.esante.gouv.fr/fhir/CodeSystem/tre-r384-pratique-therapeutique-specifique-act-de-soin-amm</code> defines the following codes:</p><table class=\"codes\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Affichage</b></td><td><b>Date de Validité</b></td><td><b>Date de mise à jour</b></td><td><b>status</b></td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">PTS00<a name=\"tre-r384-pratique-therapeutique-specifique-act-de-soin-amm-PTS00\"> </a></td><td>Pas de pratique thérapeutique spécifique</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>active</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">PTS01<a name=\"tre-r384-pratique-therapeutique-specifique-act-de-soin-amm-PTS01\"> </a></td><td>Mission de recours et chirurgie oncologique complexe y compris avec atteinte péritonéale (hors PTS d’organes ci-après)</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>active</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">PTS11<a name=\"tre-r384-pratique-therapeutique-specifique-act-de-soin-amm-PTS11\"> </a></td><td>Maxillo-faciale, stomatologie et chirurgie orale</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>active</td></tr><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">PTS12<a name=\"tre-r384-pratique-therapeutique-specifique-act-de-soin-amm-PTS12\"> </a></td><td>Orthopédique et traumatologique</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01:00</td><td>1900-01-01T00:00:00+01: